msgid ""
"On Linux, video drivers for AMD, Intel and NVIDIA (free software Nouveau) "
"are built into a single project called <b>Mesa</b>. Below you can choose a "
"Mesa variant and manage extra packages for gaming, video playback, compute "
"and AI."
